[Although genome sequence of one of the strains of the virus has been found to be somewhat similar to the variant virus circulating in the UK, as indicated in the news report above, it is reportedly not 100% the same, suggesting the need for more verification of sequence data to assess the possible introduction of the variant to the country.

The daily case positivity against the total number of samples tested over the last week in Bangladesh was just below 10%, except one day when it was slightly above 10%. - Mod.PKB

